OL,4,CTokyo Games creative head quits over
OL,5,C'Olympig' insult
OL,6, Tokyo Olympics' creative chief has
OL,7, resigned after suggesting that a female
OL,8, comedian could appear as an "Olympig",
OL,9, in the latest setback for the Games.
OL,11,FHiroshi Sasaki said plus-size
OL,12,Fentertainer Naomi Watanabe could wear
OL,13,Fpig ears at the opening ceremony.
OL,15,FHe later apologised and admitted his
OL,16,Fremarks were "a huge insult" to her. Ms
OL,17,FWatanabe has yet to respond.
OL,19,FThe incident comes after ex-Games
OL,20,Fpresident Yoshiro Mori was forced to
OL,21,Fquit for making sexist remarks.
